#
# cyclictest-latmus: A wrapper providing cyclictest-compatible interface
# using latmus (EVL/Xenomai 4) as the measurement backend.
#
# Spawns one latmus instance per CPU (like cyclictest -S) and consolidates
# per-CPU histogram data into cyclictest-compatible multi-column output.
